      <title>法国通胀率回落至三年来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/french-inflation-retreats-to-its-lowest-level-in-three-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国通胀率降至 2021 年 7 月以来的最低水平——在德国和西班牙出现类似经济放缓后，这增强了欧洲央行继续降息的理由。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-30/french-inflation-retreats-to-its-lowest-level-in-three-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 30 Aug 2024 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
